            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">37.302</ph> Bonds or other security.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p id="d2397e13" class="- topic/p ">When a contract is solely for dismantling, demolition, or removal of improvements, <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html"
                     class="- topic/xref ">40 U.S.C.chapter 31</xref>
				        </ph>, subchapter III, Bonds, (see <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="FAR-i1088557.dita#i1088557"
                     base="i1088557"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">28.102</xref>
				        </ph>) does not apply. However, the contracting officer may require the contractor to furnish a performance bond or other security (see <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="FAR-i1088629.dita#i1088629"
                     base="i1088629"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">28.103</xref>
				        </ph>) in an amount that the contracting officer considers adequate to-</p>
			      <ol id="d2386e34" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2397e38" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Ensure completion of the work;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2397e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Protect property to be retained by the Government;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2397e56" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Protect property to be provided as compensation to the contractor; and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2397e65" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Protect the Government against damage to adjoining property.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
